import React from 'react'
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar'
import { Container , Form } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Addrestaurant = () => {
  return (
    <>        
    <NavBar/>
    <Container className='col-3'>
      <Container style={{margin:'1rem auto', textAlign:'ce'}}>
        ADD RESTAURANT
      </Container>
      <Form>
        <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='restrauntName '></Form.Control>
        <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='restrauntAddress '></Form.Control>
        <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='restrauntPhoneNumber '></Form.Control>
        <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='restrauntOwnerName '></Form.Control>
        <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='restrauntOwnerPhone '></Form.Control>
        <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='restrauntOwnerEmail '></Form.Control>
      </Form>
    </Container>

    </>
  )
}

export default Addrestaurant
